HTTPPacket - Class in fr.uge.net.tcp.nonblocking.http
HTTPPacket.type : type (not null) of the packet that can be either: HTTPPacket.HTTPPacketType.REQUEST -> in this case every fields are null except HTTPPacket.resource which is the request. HTTPPacket.HTTPPacketType.BAD_RESPONSE -> in this case every fields are null except HTTPPacket.resource. HTTPPacket.HTTPPacketType.GOOD_RESPONSE -> in this case HTTPPacket.contentType contains the type of the content and HTTPPacket.content contains the content of the HTTP response (the buffer is in read-mode) and HTTPPacket.resource contains the name of the received resource.
